data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome Home! Prepare to FALL IN LOVE with this Move In Ready, Well Maintained, and Functional Haines Floor plan by Ashton Woods. Situated just steps away from miles of walking, biking, and running trails, Pond Views, Zip Line Park and Greenspace, the Dog Park, and the Community Center…you CAN’T BEAT THIS LOCATION. As you step inside you will find Beautifully Upgraded Luxury Vinyl Richwood Oak Flooring, a First Floor Bedroom with Ensuite, Oversized Storage Closet under the stairs and your Garage Entry. Your First Floor Bedroom makes for the PERFECT Office Space or Guest Suite. Your Ensuite has lovely 12x24 Tile Flooring, Quartz Counters, Shower with Floor to Ceiling Tile, and an oversized Walk In Closet. Let's head upstairs, but first how about these Stunning WOOD STAIR Treads! At the first landing you will find your half bathroom, perfectly situated off the Main Living Space. Your second story, Open Concept Family Room, Kitchen, and Dining Room Combo is the HEART OF THE HOME. Your Lovely new Kitchen has everything you need. From Light Bright Shaker style Cabinets along the perimeter and Dove on the Island, to Stainless Steel Appliances, Upgraded Features like a Trash Can Pull Out, Modern Hardware, a Single Basin Sink, and a Trendy Subway Style Backsplash. Your Large Island offers a great place for Friends and Family to gather and your Cozy Dining Room is the perfect place to sit down and enjoy a good meal. BONUS…the CUTEST OUTDOOR Balcony where you can enjoy the FLORIDA weather all year long. Let's head into your new Family Room. Spacious in Size, Versatile in space, and Large Windows offer great views and tons of Natural Light. Last but not least, let's head up stairs to the third floor to your private corridor of bedrooms. First, let's stop in your well situated Walk In Laundry Room. Next, we head into a very Large Second Bedroom with an Ensuite. Your Ensuite offers Upgraded 12x24 tile, Quartz Countertops, and a Tub Shower with Floor to Ceiling Tile. Tucked away on the other side of the hall is your Spacious Master Retreat with a Walk In Closet and UPGRADED Ensuite. This Ensuite is TASTEFULLY Designed with Stunning Dark Shaker Style Cabinets, A Drawer Stack, Gold Hardware, Single Hole Single Faucet, Modern Lighting, Frameless Shower with Oversized Subway Tile stacked horizontally from floor to ceiling, with Gold Faucets, a Shower Bench, and Dark Flooring. Lastly, this home offers a Two Car Garage. HOA Includes HIGH-SPEED INTERNET of up 1GIG, FOB entry to LP Fitness Center, Resort-Style LP Aquatic Center with Beach Volleyball Court and a half Basketball Court. Laureate Park also offers Community Gardens, Dog Parks, Playgrounds and Miles of Trails to enjoy Walking, Running and Biking. Enjoy Community Activities like Live and Local, Movies in the Park, Yoga and more. Located in the heart of Lake Nona Medical City with BEEP autonomous shuttle service. A RATED SCHOOLS and Minutes to Orlando International Airport, Major Highways, Shopping, Dining, USTA and KPMG.
